    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Ready to hit the road without a hefty price tag? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's fully functional and gets you where you need to go, but we want to be upfront that it shows its age with some visible wear on the exterior and interior. There may be a few minor mechanical items worth attention, but overall it's a solid, honest car for a budget-conscious buyer. If you're looking for reliable everyday transportation with some character, this could be a smart pick!",
