    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, dependable ride that gets the job done without the premium price tag? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives reliably, making it a great choice for daily commuting and everyday errands! You'll notice some cosmetic wear and minor imperfections that come with regular use, but nothing that gets in the way of its functionality. It's a practical, honest vehicle for the budget-savvy buyer who wants solid transportation without overpaying. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
