    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Dependable & Well-Maintained \u2013 A Solid Good-Condition Ride! \ud83d\ude97\n\nIf you're looking for a vehicle that's been genuinely cared for and is ready to take on your daily commute or weekend adventures, this one is worth a close look! It presents well inside and out, with no major issues to worry about \u2014 just honest, reliable transportation that's been kept in good shape over the years. Minor wear here and there is to be expected, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal or performance. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself \u2014 this is a car you can feel good about driving home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and we're proud to present one of the finest examples you'll find on the market today. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 the paint retains a deep, vibrant shine with no visible scratches, chips, or fading, and every body panel sits perfectly aligned. Up close, you'll find no blemishes worth mentioning; this car looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally impressive: the seats, dashboard, door panels, and carpeting are all in pristine shape with no wear, staining, or cracking to speak of. Every switch, button, and feature functions exactly as it should, and the cabin feels fresh and clean throughout. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. Service records are up to date, and the mechanical components are in excellent working order. If you've been searching for a vehicle you can drive with complete confidence from day one \u2014 with no surprises and no compromises \u2014 this is it.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a fair-condition car, and buyers should have reasonable expectations going in. The exterior shows visible wear including several scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading that is noticeable upon close inspection. The body panels are structurally intact, but cosmetic imperfections are present throughout. The interior is functional but shows clear signs of use \u2014 expect worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim pieces, and general aging consistent with a vehicle that has seen regular daily driving. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention in the near future; buyers should budget for potential maintenance or minor repairs. This is a practical option for someone who needs reliable basic transportation and is comfortable with a vehicle that has some miles and wear on it. A pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you make a decision. The exterior shows visible wear \u2014 you can expect several scratches, minor dents, and some fading to the paint in certain areas. It's not a showroom car, but it's presentable enough for everyday use. The interior has seen regular use as well, with noticeable wear on the seats, some scuffs on the trim panels, and minor staining here and there. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it has some age-related wear that a prospective buyer should be aware of \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection to fully understand its current mechanical state. There are no major structural concerns, but minor repairs or maintenance items may be needed in the near term. Overall, this is a solid, honest, workaday vehicle that will serve a buyer well if they go in with realistic expectations. Priced fairly to reflect its actual condition.",
      "price": 16500.0,
